{"tid":2295000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有大灣區「香港一定發達」 林奮強2,768萬沽聚豪天下","createTime":"2020-11-21T12:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T12:28:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db3feb30917e22772b404efb50eac151f8d0cc99","tid":2295000,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"林奮強是出名的樓市大好友，在2018年時曾在公開場合說過，發展大灣區之後「香港一定發達」，又指，香港醫療問題、土地及房屋供應的短缺問題令香港年輕人變得悲觀，狹窄的生活空間使不少年輕人渴望移民，他當時聲言，如果5年內「三項策略上都改變唔到，我都會移民」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201121/TJ3QVKELBJD3DBXPURVGI3VJEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201121%2FTJ3QVKELBJD3DBXPURVGI3VJEM%2F&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=f0954a51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201121%2FTJ3QVKELBJD3DBXPURVGI3VJEM%2F&h=5a22facc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201121/TJ3QVKELBJD3DBXPURVGI3VJEM/</a>"},{"pid":"d84bcc53b54eb7c0517c05c161acb2c0fd29be9e","tid":2295000,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"犯國安法，拉得"}]}